What's new
You and everyone else in your organization have your own profile page in Delve. Use it to find documents you and others have stored in OneDrive for Business and SharePoint in Office 365.
Get to know Delve
What you see in Delve is different from what other people see. You can only see documents if you have access to them in OneDrive for Business or SharePoint in Office 365.
